{"tid":1549020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【9月16日！求下你地唔好罷課呀！！】","createTime":"2019-09-07T07:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T14:32:52.000Z","uid":220434,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d89b4597f7ad7ed940c1afe3f017ac9fa20a163f","tid":1549020,"uid":220434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>【9月16日！求下你地唔好罷課呀！！】</strong><br />\n<br />\n代post<br />\n<br />\n每年新學年，教育局會安排一日，派人去每間中學數返學人數。而教育局已內部宣布，今年日子為9月16日。<br />\n<br />\n如果當日count到返學人數唔夠，教育局會再安排一日，再數多一次，所以只要係佢地count人數果一日罷課，一定會比到學校壓力，因為學校會面臨縮班！cut教師職員！兼且會有殺校既危機！<br />\n<br />\n雖然有啲學校都有違道德人性，但請你地唔好為左攬炒而唔返學呀<br />\n<br />\n利申: 中學AdmissionTeam<br />\n#校長副校真係會好撚緊張"},{"pid":"743ec70095b1483f62fc2236c919d053296db406","tid":1549020,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:40:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21ca0aaf24d49fc725ced19de2e0569e92a3bd98","tid":1549020,"uid":220434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0LdY99Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0LdY99Q.jpg&h=7e0040c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eec1d261ea97d08064dc9fcee97eda7cd330c238","tid":1549020,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"全香港都係16號定點?<br />\n教育局要同一日派人check晒全部學校<br />\n好似有啲難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8100567f87de56c5c89658d8fe482ad3ae1a95a","tid":1549020,"uid":220434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eec1d261ea97d08064dc9fcee97eda7cd330c238","tid":1549020,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"全香港都係16號定點?<br />\n教育局要同一日派人check晒全部學校<br />\n好似有啲難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:52:38.000Z","msg":"係全港啊"},{"pid":"e206dab0434d37c3bb5c33e69bc5126fa0ab3